import React from "react"; import "./AboutMe.css"; function AboutMe() { return (

I'm Shuohe Ren

With a passion for technology and a decade of experience under my belt, I am a seasoned software engineer who thrives in dynamic environments. Throughout my journey in the tech world, I've contributed to groundbreaking projects, collaborated with cross-functional teams, and always stayed curious.

After a wonderful trip in the US, I ventured overseas to learning Computer Science from Boston University.

When I'm not buried in code, you might find me exploring the world of classical music or catching up on the latest tech documentaries. I'm an ardent believer in continuous learning and often engage with online coding platforms to stay updated and challenge myself.

Outside of work, I even tried my hand at writing a sci-fi novel. But the thrill of solving complex problems and creating something new with just lines of code always brings me back to my keyboard.

I enjoy connecting with like-minded individuals, discussing the latest tech trends, or collaborating on innovative projects. If you're interested in getting to know more about my work or just want to chat, check out my profiles and reach out!

My GitHub My LeetCode My YouTube My Codeforces
); } export default AboutMe;
